<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Hukdampa'n ka ma A huoi,
 Thildang banga ka ngek ding?
 A hehpihna ka ginglah dem?
 Damsunga eipui pa chuh!
 Muonna nuom, Pathien lungmuonna,
 Amah gin zieka luoh ding,
 * Thil bangcheng hungtung mahlele;
 Isu'n bangcheng ei hih sak (2)

[V2]
 2. Ka Hukdampa'n ka ma A huoi,
 Kipakin ma ka chawn zel;
 Thepna ah ei panpih zela,
 Changthak hingin ei vak ie;
 Ka lenna gam chu lauhum in,
 Ka thagau dangchak mahleh;
 * Ka ma'h suongpi a hung luok dawng,
 Ngaiin nawpna lui ka mu'i (2)

[V3]
 3. Ka Hukdampa'n ka ma A huoi,
 Aw A hehpihna bukim;
 Chawlhna bukim chan thu ei tiem,
 Chunggama ka Pa In ah;
 Siet theihlohna mun ka tun tieng,
 Khawvak nuom taka lengin;
 * Zie ka kumsawt la ding ahi,
 Lal Isu'n ka ma A huoi (2)</lyrics>
<title>ALLTHE WAY</title>
</song>